# Source: cheetah_mixture_composition.dat joined with cheetah_materials.dat
# (SELFIES) and cheetah_cetane_number.dat (CN, required).
# Unused cpnt_selfies_* slots are NaN.
# Mixture order follows cheetah_mixture.dat.
# Selection: identified components <= 10, or top 10 identified volume fractions >= 95 % of total identified volume when > 10 identified components.
# Unidentified components are excluded from ranking and thresholds.
# cpnt_vol_*: volume fraction (0-1) from mixture_comp_vol (%).
